    <mainBody>
      <paragraph eId="para_1" class="PlainText">
        <content eId="para_1__content">
          <p xml:space="preserve">	On 8 March 2022, the President of the Human Rights Council, in accordance with General Assembly resolution <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/75/314">75/314</a> of 2 August 2021, announced the appointment of the following persons as members of the Permanent Forum of People of African Descent for a three-year term of office effective immediately: Gaynel Diana Curry, Huang Hongjiang, Michael McEchrane, Pastor Elías Murillo Martínez and Alice Angèle Nkom.<authorialNote marker="2" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_2"><p xml:space="preserve"> See <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/76/952">A/76/952</a>.</p></authorialNote></p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph eId="para_2" class="PlainText">
        <content eId="para_2__content">
          <p xml:space="preserve"> As a result, as of 8 March 2022, the Permanent Forum of People of African Descent is composed as follows: Epsy <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">Campbell Barr</inline> (<span class="italic">Costa Rica</span>),* Gaynel Diana <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">C</inline><inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">urry</inline> (<span class="italic">Bahamas</span>),* Justin <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">Hansford</inline> (<span class="italic">United States of America</span>),* <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">H</inline><inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">uang</inline> Hongjiang (<span class="italic">China</span>),* Martin <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">Kimani</inline> (<span class="italic">Kenya</span>),* Michael <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">McEchrane</inline> (<span class="italic">Sweden</span>),* Pastor Elías <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">Murillo Martínez</inline> (<span class="italic">Colombia</span>),* Alice Angèle <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">N</inline><inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">kom</inline> (<span class="italic">Cameroon</span>),* Mona <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">Omar</inline> (<span class="italic">Egypt</span>)* and June <inline name="smallCaps" style="font-variant:small-caps">Soomer</inline> (<span class="italic">Saint Lucia</span>).*</p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
